title: Caching Proxy Server
description: Cli tool that starts a caching proxy server. The server forwards requests to a target server and caches the responses in a sqlite file. If the same request is made again, the cached response is returned instead of forwarding the request to the target server.

title: Complete Newsletter App
description: Robust Newsletters Backend Service with Email (SMTP) and FrontEnd Dashboard

title: Gnome-Shell Extension
description: Simple Gnome extension to keep track of BTC and ETH prices against USD and EUR. Over 300 people have already downloaded it.

title: CLI Todo App
description: Simple command line todo app that allows you to create and manage a todo list. You can add, delete, mark as done, list, and report tasks using this app.
